title: 10 Takeaways from Week 10
itunes:title: 10 Takeaways from Week 10
description:
DJ and Bucky break down the week that was with their top 10 takeaways from week 10, including – Saints are Super Bowl favorites (1:00), Andrew Luck is back (5:00), Baker Mayfield’s big day (8:30), Chiefs and Rams avoid upsets before their Week 12 showdown (16:35), Trubisky looks like a franchise QB (23:10), Raiders have no playmakers (27:00), Mariota is getting comfortable & the Patriots struggles (31:35), another slow start for the Eagles (34:45), and why you shouldn’t sleep on the Redskins (36:20).
